skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
Listen to daily updates from your good health tips. You can just say "Alexa, what's my flash briefing". You can say "Alexa, stop" to exit anytime.

There are a lot of tips on the internet related to health. But you can`t tell if they are real or do any good to you. May be some are doing bad to your health. With this health tips however, you can try and feel for yourself the effects. Listen to the tips and also do not forget to try. If it helped you, listen more tips. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer. Wish for your good health.

Disclaimer : The information in this skill is provided for informational and educational purposes only and is not a substitute for professional medical advice, treatment, or diagnosis. If you think you may have a medical emergency, please dial your local emergency response phone number.
